---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Cookie Policy | jmfernxndez"
  description="Learn about the cookie policy for jmfernxndez's website. No cookies or user tracking are used, ensuring your privacy across all pages and projects."
>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Cookie Policy</h1>

    <section class="intro">
      <p>
        This Cookie Policy explains how <a
          href="https://github.com/jmfernxndez"
          target="_blank">jmfernxndez</a
        >, freelance web developer, manages cookies and tracking technologies on
        this website, including pages for projects like <a href="/web-tracker"
          >Webtracker</a
        > and <a href="/web-vitals-extension">Web Vitals</a>. My commitment is
        to protect your privacy by avoiding cookies and tracking entirely. Last
        updated: August 19, 2025.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="no-cookies">
      <h2>No Cookies or Tracking</h2>
      <p>
        This website does not use cookies, web beacons, or any other tracking
        technologies. I do not collect, store, or process any data related to
        your browsing activity on this site. This ensures a privacy-first
        experience while you explore my projects or services.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="projects">
      <h2>My Projects and Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        My Chrome extensions, including <a
          href="https://github.com/jmfernxndez/webtracker"
          target="_blank">Webtracker</a
        > and <a
          href="https://github.com/jmfernxndez/web-vitals-extension"
          target="_blank">Web Vitals</a
        >, also adhere to this no-tracking philosophy:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Webtracker</strong>: Tracks website usage time locally on your
          device without cookies or external data transmission.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Web Vitals</strong>: Monitors performance metrics (e.g., LCP,
          CLS, INP) locally in your browser, with no cookies or tracking
          involved.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        For more details on data handling, see my <a href="/privacy-policy"
          >Privacy Policy</a
        >.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="contact">
      <h2>Questions?</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions about this Cookie Policy or my projects, please
        contact me at <a href="mailto:jmfernandez@vantag.es"
          >jmfernandez@vantag.es</a
        > or visit my <a href="/contact">contact page</a>. You can also explore
        my work on my <a href="https://github.com/jmfernxndez" target="_blank"
          >GitHub profile</a
        >.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>

  <style>
    .container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 2rem;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      color: #333;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    p {
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #555;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    ul {
      list-style-type: disc;
      margin-left: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    li {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: #555;
    }
    a {
      color: #007bff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style></Layout
>
